53
00:02:15,440 --> 00:02:18,759
Kenapa harus memedulikan sisi kanan dan kiri?

54
00:02:18,759 --> 00:02:19,759
Karena aku merasa...

55
00:02:19,759 --> 00:02:21,600
Lalu, kenapa kau tidak peduli?

56
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:22,520
Kau pindah saja ke sini.

57
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:22,960
Tunggu.

58
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:23,980
(Aku bercanda denganmu)

59
00:02:25,160 --> 00:02:25,880
Kau pindah saja ke sini.

60
00:02:31,919 --> 00:02:33,479
Bagaimana ini?

61
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,360
Kita sudah berangkat.

62
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:43,119
