92
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:40,919
Benar.

93
00:03:40,919 --> 00:03:42,479
Kau bisa mencari topik.

94
00:03:42,479 --> 00:03:43,240
Bagus.

95
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,279
Jika terus dipendam,

96
00:03:44,279 --> 00:03:46,279
