Namaku Tao Zhi.

200
00:07:34,359 --> 00:07:35,320
Namaku Meng'er.

201
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:37,359
Senang berkenalan denganmu.

202
00:07:37,359 --> 00:07:38,040
Setelah kembali kali ini,

203
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:40,239
