757
00:26:43,199 --> 00:26:43,839
Tidak.

758
00:26:45,160 --> 00:26:46,319
Setelah dia kembali,

759
00:26:46,319 --> 00:26:47,680
lalu

760
00:26:47,680 --> 00:26:49,280
saat aku bertatapan dengannya semalam,

761
00:26:49,280 --> 00:26:50,920
aku sudah memastikan perasaanku bahwa aku

762
00:26:50,920 --> 00:26:51,560
tidak punya perasaan kepadanya.

763
00:26:51,560 --> 00:26:53,000
Aku mungkin hanya merasa rindu

764
00:26:53,000 --> 00:26:54,839
