765
00:26:54,839 --> 00:26:57,520
Saat Kompetisi Bertahan Hidup di awal,

766
00:26:57,520 --> 00:26:59,000
lalu ada orang yang sangat bertekad,

767
00:26:59,000 --> 00:27:00,040
maka kau akan memiliki rasa aman.

768
00:27:00,040 --> 00:27:01,079
Kemudian, setelah dia pergi,

769
00:27:01,079 --> 00:27:02,439
