770
00:27:05,680 --> 00:27:06,040
Sebentar...

771
00:27:06,040 --> 00:27:06,839
Tidak masalah, katakan saja.

772
00:27:06,839 --> 00:27:08,319
Sebentar mengobrol dengan gadis ini,

773
00:27:08,319 --> 00:27:09,599
