774
00:27:09,599 --> 00:27:11,199
Jadi, aku pun berpikir...

775
00:27:11,199 --> 00:27:13,280
Lalu, aku pun punya perasaan lebih terhadapmu,

776
00:27:13,280 --> 00:27:14,800
