854
00:30:02,430 --> 00:30:03,520
Aku memotong sedikit untuk kalian.

855
00:30:04,070 --> 00:30:04,830
Terima kasih.

856
00:30:04,830 --> 00:30:05,680
Ayo.

857
00:30:05,680 --> 00:30:07,590
Rasanya seperti bertamu ke rumah mereka.

858
00:30:07,590 --> 00:30:09,040
