Ambillah sedikit.

859
00:30:09,040 --> 00:30:10,470
Makanlah jeruk dingin.

860
00:30:10,470 --> 00:30:11,280
Apakah dingin?

861
00:30:11,800 --> 00:30:12,280
Ya, dingin.

862
