893
00:31:01,800 --> 00:31:03,000
Seharusnya tidak ada.

894
00:31:04,760 --> 00:31:05,190
Oke.

895
00:31:06,190 --> 00:31:07,310
Beres.

896
00:31:07,310 --> 00:31:08,280
Terima kasih.

897
00:31:08,280 --> 00:31:08,680
Oke.

898
00:31:09,640 --> 00:31:10,830
