903
00:31:24,310 --> 00:31:25,710
Ini roti untukmu.

904
00:31:26,160 --> 00:31:27,190
Terima kasih.

905
00:31:27,640 --> 00:31:29,400
Aku mengambilkanmu sebotol air.

906
00:31:29,400 --> 00:31:30,350
Terima kasih.

907
